videos.headline: McClesky Jr. runs in for 3-yd TD
videos.description: Eastern Kentucky's Daryl McClesky Jr. runs the ball straight into the end zone for a 3-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Doege finds Morris for 24-yd Bowling Green TD
videos.description: Bowling Green's Jarret Doege connects with Quintin Morris in the end zone for a 24-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: EKU's MCleskey Jr. takes off for 68-yd TD run
videos.description: Eastern Kentucky's Daryl McCleskey Jr. runs 68 yards down the field for a touchdown, tying the game against Bowling Green.
